<td>A black long-haired domestic cat capable of changing the physical form of entities within 30&#160;m of it and influencing thought processes of humans within effective range. SCP-795' uses these abilities to satisfy basic needs and desires consistent with that of a wasp of the <em>Pompilidae</em> taxonomic family (commonly referred to as tarantula hawks). SCP-795' is capable of transferring these abilities to other cats on a permanent basis.</td>
